title: League of Legends Tower Analysis
description: Deep dive in statistical League of Legends tower analysis data. See how the impacts of toweres on the game change over time.

title: Does National Debt Determine Quality of Life?
description: How does a nation's debt impact the quality of life of its citizens? This project aims to analyze the correlation between national debt and quality of life indicators.

title: Bullet Hell Game
description: A bullet hell game where the player must dodge a barrage of bullets while trying to defeat enemies. The game features multiple levels, power-ups, and challenging boss fights. Created in unity and C#.

title: LetterGen
description: How might chatGPT be used to generate personalized and tailored letters for different occasions? This project explores the prompting process and the results of using chatGPT to generate letters.

title: Grocery Store Visualization
description: What makes an effective visualization of where to buy your groceries? This project goes through the process of creating an effective visualization comparing different grocery stores and their prices.
